  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: ec9a774f1c3f94c5ab3b77c67ac7f734, type: 3}
  m_Name: LoopReflect_05
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ReflectBranch
  lines:
  - "I\u2019m stuck!"
  - I am officially STUCK in a LOOP.
  - How am I gonna get out of this?
  - Unless... this is the universe's sick way of helping me out?
  - Giving me unlimited tries at asking Daisy to the dance?
  - "If she says YES, maybe I\u2019ll stop looping!"
  - "That\u2019s not the craziest theory I could think of\u2026"
  - Asking her SO FAR has been absolutely TERRIFYING.
  - I feel my confidence draining just walking up to her!
  - "I could only get in a good conversation with her\u2026"
  - Start feeling comfortable...
  - Build my confidence up...
  - MAYBE I could do this.
  - And, you know...
  - Not die.
  - "Again\u2026"
  - "Yep, let\u2019s go with that."
  - Now THINK! What else can I say to her?
